import Page from "../common/Page" import classes from "./PostDetailPage.module.css" import { useParams } from 'react-router-dom'; import { useState, useEffect } from "react" import {getRoomListApi} from '../../../api/RoomApi' const landlord = { list: "50", cover: "https://funny-daffodil-350bc9.netlify.app/images/customer/team-1.jpg", address: "Liverpool, Canada", name: "Sargam S. Singh", icon: [, , , ], } const data = { id: 1, cover: "https://funny-daffodil-350bc9.netlify.app/images/list/p-1.png", name: "Red Carpet Real Estate", location: "210 Zirak Road, Canada", category: "For Rent", price: "$3,700", type: "Apartment", } const typeData = [ { text: "Family House", value: "Family House" }, { text: "House & Villa", value: "House & Villa" }, { text: "Apartment", value: "Apartment" }, { text: "Office & Studio", value: "Office & Studio" }, { text: "Villa & Condo", value: "Villa & Condo" }, ] const PostDetailPage = () => { const params = useParams() const id = params.id const [post, setPost] = useState({}) useEffect(() => { getRoomListApi({ "id": id }) .then((data) => { const tempData = [] data.data.forEach(item => { tempData.push({ cover: `https://funny-daffodil-350bc9.netlify.app/images/list/p-1.png`, totalPrice: item.rent_price + item.water_price + item.electricity_price + item.service_price, location: `${item.city} - ${item.district} - ${item.ward}`, ...item }) }) setPost(tempData[0]) console.log(tempData[0]) }) .catch((err) => { alert(err.message); }); }, [id]) return (

{post.room_name}

{post.location}

{post.detail}

{landlord.name}

    {landlord.icon.map((icon, index) => (
  • {icon}
    • ))}
) } export default PostDetailPage
